'''= Histories about art in the Basque context told by the own artists and cultural agents'''

URL = http://www.wiki-historias.org

==Description==
WIKI-HISTORIES is a experiment to build histories of art in the Basque Country encouraging women artist and cultural agents to provide their testimonies about their own experiences and perspectives in relation to art in the Basque context adding these pieces of knowledge to a shared on-line space. Moreover, several presencial events have been organized, such us visiting tours to the public art collection the Fine Art Museum of Bilbao from a feminist perspective, workshops and presentations. Right now the initiative is taking part of Plataforma A, periodical encounters to work  about equalitarian opportunities of women artist in the art field.

